{"tid":2256494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑狗o係荃灣又鳩拉","createTime":"2020-10-24T11:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T04:39:00.000Z","uid":51271,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b3c11adac3f29e7597aa1b39c581c54f657019b4","tid":2256494,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:42:52.000Z","msg":"賢學思政荃灣街站 警拉兩女子入橙帶區 指控違限聚令】<br />\n<br />\n現場直播：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HuY2HJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HuY2HJ&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=0c0b63ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HuY2HJ</a><br />\n<br />\n學生組織賢學思政今午聯同荃灣區議員陳劍琴於荃灣地皇廣場外擺設抗爭攝影展，及街站籲公眾關注 12 港人。警員兩度以「橙帶」圍封現場，截查街站義工，警告市民或違限聚令。<br />\n<br />\n在第二次圍封當中，4 名工作人員被橙帶圍起，然後警員再從另一邊卓悅化妝品店門口，將兩名女子拉入橙帶區內，指違反限聚令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3583733108378950/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3583733108378950%2F&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=d3840281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3583733108378950/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/122194422_3583733115045616_8891314545713112056_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=vg4tyXDYR-QAX9wKhVp&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-2.xx&amp;oh=13d19ec4ec567d821a0ee0aad7f0def9&amp;oe=5FB7EA4E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F122194422_3583733115045616_8891314545713112056_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3Dvg4tyXDYR-QAX9wKhVp%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-2.xx%26oh%3D13d19ec4ec567d821a0ee0aad7f0def9%26oe%3D5FB7EA4E&h=f4070fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">有片做backup，上庭抗辯</span>"},{"pid":"bf4dba11d8d87690f21dc66ba159157b8c3bb3dc","tid"